title: ANNE with an 'E' - You Can Ride in Back (Piano Cover)
description:
I just finished watching this more than amazing series. It's very rare that shows get better as they get older but it is the case with ANNE. And to find out that it was stupidly cancelled at the peak of its art. So frustrating. Please go sign the petition so we can have another season! None of the stories are concluded, Netflix needs to fix this! Anyways, the music is gorgeous and I hope to make more covers of different pieces in the next few days. 
I hope you like it.
Thanks for watching!!!
